image_analysis.description: A photograph of a small storage closet or utility room. The room is filled with various cardboard boxes and office/maintenance supplies stacked on metal-bracketed wall shelves and on the floor. Items include light bulb boxes (Philips, Sylvania), locksets (U.S. Lock), and various unmarked brown shipping boxes. A black computer tower or electronic device is visible on the floor. The walls are off-white, and the floor is a light-colored speckled tile. A white door is partially open on the right side of the frame.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a storage area with L-shaped shelving units.
